reviewText: I really enjoyed the DVD, great information and great drama- it showed a true reality of what would happen after an EMP and the situation people would be facing in a neighborhood, etc.
Title: Remnants

reviewText: Everyone should be watching this movie & paying attention to what is going on out there.  It won't hurt to be ready.
Title: Remnants

reviewText: Tom struggles through this flick, cheap sets...however if you like character studies on mental collapse, you'll like this one. Sadly Sizemore acts like he wishes he was elsewhere than on the set of this 'B' movie. There are some ok moments and some interesting characters that never quite got developed, but it is, what it is...a 'B' movie.
Title: Remnants

reviewText: Dull, boring, sleep inducing.  The plot drags and was so obvious.  The "White House group" are real amateurs.  We turned it off before it was over.  Tom Sizemore must have been embarrassed with his role.
summary: Don't waste your time unless your are an Insomniac and need something to put you into a deep sleep.
Title: Remnants
